data.name: Solabia Group
data.description:
The Solabia Group serves the cosmetics, pharmacy, nutrition, biotechnology and microbiological diagnosis sectors with an extensive range of actives and ingredients. Solabia’s products are used throughout the world by the cosmetics, pharmaceutical and food industries.
Expertise in biocatalysis, enzymatic synthesis, fermentation and plant extraction has enabled Solabia to create innovative products as well as partnerships with customers and internationally renowned research organizations while maintaining a commitment to sustainable development.

data.name: Fucogel
data.description: Fucogel® Powder contains L-fucose, D-galactose and galacturonic acid and is used in the form of a powder with a non-GMO maltodextrin carrier. Fucogel® is an anionic polysaccharide with a high molecular weight (1.106 Da) obtained by bacterial fermentation from non-GMO vegetable substrates.

data.name: Fucocert
data.description: Fucocert® contains L-fucose, D-galactose and galacturonic acid and is used in the form of a solution at 1% (w/w) in water.

data.name: Nutrimel
data.description: Rich in complex sugars and minerals with humectants and moisturizing properties, Nutrimel Skin is a short and long term moisturizer, stimulating cells metabolism confronted to a stress and making their recovery easier.

data.name: BlueShield
data.description: BlueShield® is an Eco-friendly active ingredient rich in capsanthin and capsanthin esters, specific and highly effective carotenoids. It is obtained from cold pressing of red bell peppers and stabilized with vegetable glycerin and xanthan gum. Grown in France, red bell peppers come from a responsible producer, committed for a long time in environmental protection.

data.name: Fucogel® 1.5P
data.description: Fucogel® 1.5P is a purified biotechnological anionic polysaccharide (mean molecular weight 106 Da) prepared through bacterial fermentation. It is a linear structure with a saccharide sequence comprising galacturonic acid, L-fucose, and D-galactose. Fucogel has immediate and remnant moisturizing and restructuring properties, which combine to create remarkable sensory power, providing comfort and softness to cosmetic formulae during and after application. It is available in 1% (w/w) in water.

data.name: BioEcolia®
data.description: BioEcolia® is a glucan oligosaccharide obtained through enzymatic synthesis from natural sugars (sucrose and maltose). It is used to protect and stimulate natural skin defenses, serving as a bioselective substrate for beneficial skin flora while inhibiting the growth of pathogens and other undesirable flora. It provides gentle protective and restoring action for all types of skin and scalp.

data.name: Seboxyl®
data.description: Seboxyl® is a vegetal juice of fresh organic blackcurrant (Ribes nigrum) and raspberry (Rubus idaeus) leaves, obtained through cold pressing in a non-denaturing condition, with organic vegetal glycerin. 99.8% of the total ingredients are of natural origin, and 99.55% are from organic farming.

data.name: Glycofilm® 1.5P
data.description: Glycofilm® 1.5P is an anionic polysaccharide with a branched, desacetylated structure that is obtained through bacterial fermentation of vegetal sorbitol and autolytic yeast extract. This product serves as a second-skin interactive protective matrix, allowing for a balanced protection and pleasure while maintaining a new relationship with one's skin. It is a non-occlusive, transparent, and natural body/face shield that protects the skin from the surrounding environment.

data.name: PHYTOCARE-HA™ CG 1M
data.description: PHYTOCARE-HA™ CG 1M is a COSMOS-approved biological active extracted from snow mushrooms. It has played a prominent role in Chinese history as a celebrated ingredient in herbal, cosmetic, and culinary applications. It features powerful hydration, film-forming, and anti-oxidation properties, making it very suitable for anti-aging, anti-pollution, and urban defense formulations.

data.name: Glycolysat® of Fucus UP
data.description: Glycolysat® of Fucus UP is a hydroglycolic extract prepared from the thallus of wrack (Fucus vesiculosus), a brown seaweed, obtained through controlled extraction with a propylene glycol/water mixture. This yellow-brown to gray-orange extract is recommended for use in cosmetic applications.

data.name: Glycolysat® of Baerii Caviar UP
data.description: Glycolysat® of Baerii Caviar UP is a hydroglycolic extract prepared from caviar (sturgeon eggs, Acipenser baerii) by controlled extraction using propylene glycol and water. This product appears as a translucent to opaque solution with several layers when at rest, and has a characteristic odor. It is miscible in water and 50% v/v alcohol, and it finds major applications in cosmetic products.

data.name: MATILOOK®
data.description: MATILOOK® is an active ingredient obtained through hydroglycerination of quince leaves (Cydonia oblonga) and titrated with astringent molecules. It is designed to revitalize the appearance of oily skin, refining the skin's texture and reducing shine. This product can be used in daily skin care for oily skin, facial makeup, and anti-aging skin care.

data.name: 3Dermilyn®
data.description: 3Dermilyn® is a plant polysaccharide extracted from the seeds of plantains grown in France. This organic and sustainable source is rich in mucilage. 3Dermilyn® restructures the skin's architecture, acts on the mechanisms that contribute to feelings of wellbeing, and relaxes the skin while visibly reducing the signs of aging.

data.name: Intensely Radiant Sun Gloss Lip Lacquer, SPF 20+
data.description: This highly pigmented, radiant lip lacquer enjoys dual benefits - the color payoff of a lipstick along with the vivid sheen of a lip gloss. Features intense color pop along with SPF 20 + protection.

data.name: Natural Fusion CC Cream, SPF 40, Ivory Beige
data.description: Natural Fusion is a lightweight, water-in-oil CC cream made from clean ingredient sources. Uniform, medium-to-high coverage with excellent sensory and SPF 40 broad spectrum protection

data.name: Clear N' Effervescent Scent Shampoos
data.description:
Normally shampoos with 3% perfume or higher will lose clarity, viscosity, or foaming. Our Clear n’ Effervescent Shampoos demonstrate that you can
create transparent, high viscosity shampoos in both sulfate and sulfate-free systems even with the addition of strong fragrance loads. These shampoos are clear and shear resistant with excellent soft flow, without any of that gummy afterfeel associated with traditional thickeners.

data.name: Clean Guard SPF 50 Water-free Sunscreen
data.description:
A pure, clean mineral sunscreen that doesn’t depend on unrealiable SPF boosters to reach SPF 50+. It features improved transparency over
traditional SPF 50 mineral sunscreens with little to no drag during application.

data.name: Invisiglide Sunscreen Stick
data.description: A dramatic improvement over old sunscreen stick technology, this formulation glides on smoothly and transparently with none of the traditional waxy, whitening residue. This stick features strong stability and efficient broad spectrum protecetion, requiring only 20% zinc oxide actives to achieve SPF 40.

data.name: Nature Silk Sunscreen, SPF 30+ Broad Spectrum
data.description: A 100% natural water-in-oil sunscreen with a silky smooth texture and great spreadability. Overall sensory is incredibly light with no tacky afterfeel or residual whiteness.

data.name: Sheer Invisible Natural Sunscreen, SPF 30+, Broad Spectrum
data.description: The Sheer Invisible is our most popular sunscreen prototype, and with good reason. It is a 100% natural mineral formula featuring fantastic transparency and smooth, light sensory in a stable oil-in-water emulsion.

data.name: Snow Dew Hydrating Sun Cushion, SPF 50
data.description: This is an SPF 50 water-in-oil emulsion designed to have thin, light viscosity yet still retains strong formulation stability. It features a refreshing burst of hydration upon initial application.

data.name: Vanishing Veil Mineral Primer, SPF 15 Broad Spectrum
data.description: Vanishing Veil Mineral Primer SPF 15, Broad Spectrum (CC F-017 v2) Begin your makeup routine with the perfect palette! This primer features effortless coverage with a gossamer, powdery afterfeel.

data.name: 24 Hour Super Moisturizing Night Cream
data.description: A rich, glossy white night cream that looks heavy but disperses lightly on the skin with hydrogel freshness. Sensogel 200 and Phytocare HA allow you to use low cost emollients to boost hydration while still retaining high end sensory.

data.name: Milk Becoming Water Anti-Aging Serum
data.description: This formulation illustrates the “transforming texture” concept trend - a light, milky serum that dissipates into water upon contact with skin. This  hydrating serum features fast absorption with a nontacky, silky afterfeel.

data.name: Non-Emulsifier Hydrating Face Lotion
data.description: An emulsifer-free face lotion with a lighter, water-fresh texture than conventional lotions on the market. Fast absorbing with a refreshing, hydrating afterfeel, this lotion features that high end sensory profile while using only low cost emollients like glycerin and mineral oil.

data.name: Emulsion Plus Lively Lip Trio
data.description: This unique emulsion-based lipstick combines the dense color coverage of a lipstick, the smooth moisturization of a lip balm, and the reflective water shine of a lip gloss in a single stable stick formulation.

data.name: Buttery Smooth Cleansing Balm
data.description: The Buttery Smooth Cleansing Balm is a new type of textured balm that combines a cushioned, gel-like pickup with a soft, shear-thinning sensory during application. No more crinkly cleansing balms with that waxy, candle-like feel! Also features a warming sensation during application to help open up pores for a deeper clean.

data.name: Root Deep Conditioning and Repair Serum
data.description: A lightweight, 4-in-1 hair serum that provides glossy shine, deep cuticle hair repair, superior conditioning and anti-frizz benefits.

data.name: Intensely Hydrating Lip Balm Treatment V.3
data.description: This innovative lip balm uses a water-inoil emulsion base to provide dramatically more hydration than the standard waxbased formulations. The combination of nourishing water soluble actives and emollients with OleoFlex structurants allows for increased hydration and overall stability.

data.name: FUCO-Shower
data.description: No passing on skin hydration even after a shower! The alliance of a fruity sweet pleasure and the sensoriality, Fuco-Shower will cover you with silk and leave your skin wanting for more!

data.name: FUCO-Splits
data.description: Giving refreshing care of splits with no rinse, Fuco-Splits penetrates where the hair is damaged. The refreshing and protective action of Fucogel®, along with its effect on the surface of hair improvement, gives the hair a good slicking effect. Combinated to the Silk Milk, Fuco-Splits gives the hair a light styling effect while bringing a silky touch.

data.name: Nutri 20-35 for Men
data.description: Do you search for protection and vitality? This care is yours! Nutri 20/35 For Men is a moisturizing emulsion for the urbersexual men. Ceramidone® and Glycofilm® restore the skin's barrier functions. As for Aquaregul-K®, it regulates water flow in order to boost cells.

data.name: Pure Honey Exfoliating Glycerin Cleanser
data.description: A mildly exfoliating, hydrating cleanser that reinvents the old Neutrogena formulation. It features a unique springy texture that imparts a pleasant warming sensation without any tacky afterfeel. Leave your skin feeling clean, smooth and hydrated!

data.name: Snow Kiss Hydration Concentrate
data.description: A luxuriously rich, concentrated serum that delivers intense hydration with a unique cooling effect during application. Absorbs quickly with a smooth, non-tacky afterfeel, and leaves distinctive “second skin” hydrating film with anti-irritation benefits.

data.name: Super Hydrating Mousse Mask
data.description: A soft, ultra-smooth facial mask with a unique mousse texture. This mask is deeply moisturizing with a fresh afterfeel. Just apply for 15 to 20 minutes until it dries out, then gently rinse off with water.

data.name: Your Best Natural Look Mousse Mascara
data.description: A long lasting, smudge-resistant mascara featuring a gel-like mousse texture with impressively high water resistance. The sensorial profile is light and non-waxy with a more natural feel. This is a nonclumping mascara that boosts length and volume of eyelashes.

data.name: Bouncy Cream Eye Shimmer
data.description: This eye shimmer has a unique transforming texture type of feature - the shimmer has an easy, gel-like pickup for easier control that transforms into a feathery, powdery sensory during application. It also contains new dispersion technology that allows formulators to greatly boost effect pigment usage, creating a stronger and more reflective shimmer effect on the skin.

data.name: Color Control Air Cushion Compact Broad Spectrum SPF 50+
data.description: The innovative multi-functional compact made famous by Amore Pacific. The original Amore Pacific formulation was made possible by the inclusion of Applecare A-100 (1st generation), as it helped transform a thick CC cream into a light, silky, flowable product. This updated version features a number of newer Applechem technologies to help increase hydration and formulation stability.

data.name: Highlight Your Lips Stunning Splash Lipstick, SPF 15+
data.description: This densely pigmented lipstick features a creamy, lightweight sensory during application. It is stable despite the high pigment load which allows it to retain a stunning, intensive color pop on the lips while remaining durable and heat tolerant.

data.name: Natural Look Moisturizing Lip Gloss Pot
data.description: A smooth. non-tacky lip gloss featuring excellent pick up and natural looking shine. Glossy, flexible film forming action seals in moisture and greatly increases wear while hydrating chapped lips.

data.name: Shimmering Luminosity Strobing Highlighter
data.description: This brilliant highlighter features a smooth, silky sensory, great spreadability and an illuminating finish. The pay off is excellent with smudge-free wear.

data.name: Skin Perfecting Setting Powder
data.description: Talc-free setting powder with a smooth, creamy, weightless finish. It has an anticaking feature that prevents clumps and allows seamless blend into the foundation. Apply just the right amount to prevent that thick, unnatural look under bright lights.

data.name: Sunglow Bronzer Stick
data.description: This creamy bronzer stick is the complete package - brighten and define with one-pass coverage with long lasting glow. Easy to blend in with great spreadability.

data.name: Weightless Liquid Foundation
data.description: Weightless Liquid Foundation (CC F-016 v2) A “zero gravity” liquid foundation that feels virtually weightless yet provides full, even coverage. Best of all, it still remains completely stable despite how lightweight it feels.

data.name: Arganflex Hold Conditioning Gel
data.description: ArganFlex Hold Conditioning Gel (H-SX 005) A lightweight, 3-in-1 hair gel that provides glossy shine, more natural-looking hold and superior conditioning.

data.name: Smoothie Body Butter
data.description: Smoothie Body Butter that lives up to the name - the same look and texture of cold butter straight from the fridge combined with a refreshing hydrogel feel during application. Non-greasy, velvety smooth afterfeel that softens skin and absorbs very quickly.

data.name: Soft and Bouncy Body Scrub
data.description: Unstable scrubs of the past - this soft, flexible, cushioned scrub can be squeezed out of a tube without any oil leakage whatsoever. Its supple texture is more pleasant to apply while also acting as a film former, helping to retain fragrance as well as natural oils on the skin.

data.name: Super Fresh Aqueous Day Cream
data.description: A “K-Beauty” style day cream featuring that characteristic water light freshness upon application. A unique feature is the high glycerin content for dvanced moisturization without any of the traditional tackiness associated with glycerin usage.
